<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for Subscribing</title>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .banner {
            position: relative;
        }
        .banner img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }
        .overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .overlay img {
            max-width: 50%;
            max-height: 35%;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #ffd700;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="banner">
            <img src="/assets/banner.jpg" alt="Heroes of Penta">
            <div class="overlay">
                <img src="/assets/title.png" alt="Heroes of Penta Title">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Welcome to the Heroes of Penta!</h1>
            <p>
                Thank you for subscribing to our newsletter! Get ready to dive into the thrilling tales, magical updates, and exclusive insights from the world of Penta.
            </p>
            <p>
                Stay tuned for your first epic update, and may your journey be ever victorious!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
